examples.en: This book is, to put it baldly, an uneven work.
examples.ru: Эта книга является, прямо скажем, неровной.

examples.en: He covered his bald head with a baseball cap.
examples.ru: Он прикрыл свою лысую голову бейсболкой.

examples.en: All of his uncles are completely bald.
There's a bald spot on the top of his head.
